					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13299837#post-4639019</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13299837/scp-5835#post-4639019</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 09 May 2020 17:19:25 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Nagiros</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4665703</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>It should be noted that Junior Researcher Jacobs became an instance of SCP-5835-A by writing this article.</p> </blockquote> <blockquote> <p>Additionally, as demonstrated by SCP-5835-13 and corresponding behavioral citations, SCP-5835 is unaffected by blunt-force trauma and gunfire.</p> </blockquote> <p>Ah, well this is a treat, isn't it? The description is particularly strong but the logs lag a little; there just isn't the same sort of cleverness throughout.</p> <p>Still, upvoted happily. If this is some kind of &quot;King in Yellow&quot; reference then I'm unfamiliar with the source material, so I didn't get it.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
